Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "idPerso": "{{uuidPerso}}",
    "idQuete": "{{uuidQuete}}"
}

### Voir le journal de quete d'un personnage

GET {{baseUrl}}/persoquete/{{uuidPerso}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

@uuidPersoQuete = a1bb5585-c57e-4de0-8c68-364e5cad8e53

